0.title: Connection Status
0.query:
timeseries status = avg(vmware.host.connected.status), by: { `dt.entity.vmware:host` }
| fieldsAdd entityName(`dt.entity.vmware:host`)
| sort arrayAvg(status) desc
| limit 20
